# ==========================================
# GITIGNORE PARA PROYECTO .NET (CLEAN ARCHITECTURE)
# ==========================================

# ------------------------------------------
# Carpetas de Compilación y Salida (Build & Outputs)
# ------------------------------------------
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Oo]ut/
[Aa]rtifacts/
**/[Bb]in/
**/[Oo]bj/
**/[Oo]ut/
**/[Aa]rtifacts/
publish/
[Pp]ublished/
*.Publish.xml
*.publishsettings

# ------------------------------------------
